title: The Bird And The Bee - 2007 - The Bird And The Bee [FLAC]
description:
The Bird and the Bee is the self-titled debut album by the American indie/pop music duo The Bird and the Bee. Released in early 2007, the album, containing three tracks which appeared on the band's 2006 EP Again and Again and Again and Again, received positive reviews from music critics. The first single, "Fucking Boyfriend", was a number-one hit on the U.S. Hot Dance Club Play chart in 2006.
